originalText.text: CUDA is a remarkable Dental Facility. ALL doctors whom I've encountered are just professional, warm n comforting. Dr. Shaw is just that doctor. I pray they stay open indefinitely. Facility immaculately clean, dental work is done perfect n with care. I luv luv this facility.

originalText.text: Dr. Shaw is an exceptional dentist.  She is totally dedicated to patient care and comfort.  She explained what my procedure involved and was concerned at all times with my comfort.  She was not my dentist before the procedure but I have asked her, and she has agreed, to be my dentist from now on.  I feel very fortunate to have encountered her.
